         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits. To Thetis, well-deserving daughter. Hermofilus, (her)
               heir, and Hygia—(her) parents—arranged (this) construction. She lived for twenty-one
               years.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p> Line 6: f(e)c(erunt) (Tuck).</p>
